headline: Textron Elects Cristina Méndez to Board of Directors
summary: PROVIDENCE, R.I., February 02, 2026--Cristina Méndez has been elected to Textron's Board of Directors, effective February 15, 2026.

headline: 1 Oversold Stock Ready to Bounce Back and 2 We Question
summary: Hitting a new 52-week low can be a pivotal moment for any stock. These floors often mark either the beginning of a turnaround story or confirmation that a company faces serious headwinds.
